des:
Use your voice in conjunction with Amazon Alexa to control your Leona™ Smart Home Products! Create automations for these products within the app or use your voice for live control.

(1). Download our “Leona Smart” app in the app store and register your account;
(2). Configure your Leona devices in our “Leona Smart” app and edit to the appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download the "Amazon Alexa" app from Android, iOS or Amazon App Store, then configure Echo with the Alexa app;
(4). Search “Leona Smart” skill from the Alexa app skills category;
(5). Enable “Leona Smart” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Leona Smart” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now setup is complete. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on dining room light."
"Alexa, turn off kitchen light."
"Alexa, set patio light brightness to 20%."
"Alexa, change holiday lights to red."
